This package contains snapshot builds of the LinuxSampler standalone
application, the LinuxSampler VST and AU plugins and the Fantasia and
QSampler GUI front-end applications.

Installation instructions
=========================

Copy the files in the lib folder to /usr/local/lib, or drag and drop
the lib folder to your home folder. This step is required.

Drag and drop the LinuxSampler folder to /Applications.

If you want to use the AU plugin, drag and drop
LinuxSamplerAU.component to /Library/Audio/Plug-Ins/Components.

If you want to use the VST plugin, drag and drop LinuxSampler.vst to
/Library/Audio/Plug-Ins/VST.
